OL,3,CStorms and soaring fuel prices: How
OL,4,Cdoes all this impact your Easter
OL,5,Cweekend?
OL,7,FWith rising fuel prices - and a named
OL,8,Fstorm on the way - businesses in
OL,9,FCumbria and the south of Scotland are
OL,10,Fhoping people won't be put off
OL,11,Fvisiting the region this bank holiday
OL,12,Fweekend.
OL,14,FTens of thousands of people are
OL,15,Fexpected to head to the Lake District
OL,16,Fover the next few days, and Cumbria's
OL,17,Ftourist trade will be hoping for a
OL,18,Fbumper bank holiday weekend.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
