OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775481061
OL,3,CStorms and soaring fuel prices: How
OL,4,Cdoes all this impact your Easter
OL,5,Cweekend?
OL,7,FBut as petrol prices soar and flights
OL,8,Fto and from the UK continue to be
OL,9,Fimpacted by the conflict in the Middle
OL,10,FEast, the question is, will this be
OL,11,Faffecting people's travel plans?
OL,13,FOne business owner in Windermere says
OL,14,Fit has.
OL,16,F"We've already had a couple of
OL,17,Fbookings cancel because of a flight
OL,18,Fdisruption essentially, coming through
OL,19,Fthe Middle East or from the Middle
OL,20,FEast," explains Niall Mellonie of Laik
OL,21,FHoliday Lets.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775481061
OL,3,CStorms and soaring fuel prices: How
OL,4,Cdoes all this impact your Easter
OL,5,Cweekend?
OL,7,F"But the good news is we've rebooked
OL,8,Fthem pretty much instantly, because
OL,9,Fit's quite a strong demand at the
OL,10,Fmoment for the Lakes. We have seen a
OL,11,Fcouple of people cancel as well
OL,12,Fbecause they simply couldn't afford
OL,13,Fthe fuel domestically."
OL,15,FSo, here's all you need to know ahead
OL,16,Fof the big Easter getaway this weekend:
OL,18,FIt seems the rise in fuel prices isn't
OL,19,Fputting off motorists, with the AA
OL,20,Fpredicting this Easter to be the
OL,21,Fbusiest since 2022.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
