CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775481061
OL,3,CStorms and soaring fuel prices: How
OL,4,Cdoes all this impact your Easter
OL,5,Cweekend?
OL,7,FWith flights abroad being delayed and
OL,8,Fcancelled - many people may be
OL,9,Fchoosing to holiday closer to home.
OL,11,FHowever, the organisation believes
OL,12,Fthose hitting the roads this weekend
OL,13,Fwill be shopping around for the
OL,14,Fcheapest prices at the pumps, and
OL,15,Fkeeping their journeys short.
OL,17,FTheir research has found just 5% are
OL,18,Fplanning journeys between 50 and 100
OL,19,Fmiles.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
