OL,3,CStorms and soaring fuel prices: How
OL,4,Cdoes all this impact your Easter
OL,5,Cweekend?
OL,7,FEdmund King, President of the AA told
OL,8,FITV Border: "The higher fuel prices
OL,9,Fare really going to hit home with
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,F"There's a great variety across the
OL,13,Fregion, even in Carlisle there can be
OL,14,Fa 6p a litre difference."
OL,16,FSo, how do you find the cheapest? He
OL,17,Fsays: "there are plenty of apps out
OL,18,Fthere to find the best deal."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
