OL,3,CStorms and soaring fuel prices: How
OL,4,Cdoes all this impact your Easter
OL,5,Cweekend?
OL,7,FThe AA President also believes drivers
OL,8,Fcan can save up to 10% of their fuel
OL,9,Fby reducing speeds and driving more
OL,10,Fsmoothly.
OL,12,FSo how do prices compare in our region?
OL,14,FIn Carlisle:JUnleaded 149.9 - 156.9
OL,15,F(M6 Todhill 169.9)JDiesel 179.9 `
OL,16,F186.9 (M6 Moss Connect 189.9 & Todhill
OL,17,F191.9)
OL,19,FIn Kendal:JUnleaded 151.9 ` 155.9 (M6
OL,20,FKillington 179.9)JDiesel 182.9 ` 187.9
OL,21,F(M6 Killington 195.9)
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
