OL,3,CStorms and soaring fuel prices: How
OL,4,Cdoes all this impact your Easter
OL,5,Cweekend?
OL,7,FIn Dumfries:JUnleaded 150.9 - 159.9
OL,8,FDiesel 182.5 ` 191.9
OL,10,FThe Border region is set to experience
OL,11,Fa named storm over the bank holiday
OL,12,Fweekend.
OL,14,FThe Met Office says: "Storm Dave has
OL,15,Fbeen named and is forecast to bring
OL,16,Fdamaging winds across northern parts
OL,17,Fof the UK."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
