OL,3,CStorms and soaring fuel prices: How
OL,4,Cdoes all this impact your Easter
OL,5,Cweekend?
OL,7,FYellow warnings for wind have been
OL,8,Fissued, covering all of Scotland and
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland, as well as large
OL,10,Fswathes of northern England and north
OL,11,FWales.
OL,13,FA wind warning is in place from 7pm on
OL,14,FSaturday to 7am on Easter Sunday.
OL,16,FIt is just one part of a very mixed
OL,17,FEaster forecast which will bring heavy
OL,18,Fdownpours alongside spells of warm
OL,19,Fsunshine.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
