OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775481061
OL,3,CStorms and soaring fuel prices: How
OL,4,Cdoes all this impact your Easter
OL,5,Cweekend?
OL,7,FThose coming to the Lake District
OL,8,Fmight just be wanting to tick of a
OL,9,FWainwright or two, but walkers are
OL,10,Fbeing asked to consider this carefully
OL,11,Fby the Lake District Search and
OL,12,FMountain Rescue Association
OL,14,FNick Owen told ITV Border: "Maybe,
OL,15,Fjust maybe Saturday is a day for a
OL,16,Flower level valley walk, or a visit to
OL,17,Fsome coffee shops. The high fells have
OL,18,Fbeen around for thousands of years and
OL,19,Fwill be here still when the weather
OL,20,Fimproves.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
